snippet: North Korea’s rocket launch reinforced the idea among its people that despite isolation and sanctions, the Kim dynasty is on the right track.
abstract: Analysts say reputation of Kim Jong-un, North Korea's inexperienced young leader, was likely bolstered by successful launching of long-range rocket.
lead_paragraph: North Korea’s rocket launch reinforced the idea among its people that despite isolation and sanctions, the Kim dynasty is on the right track.

headline.seo: Kim Jong-un’s Image Bolstered by Rocket Launching
headline.main: Kim Jong-un Earns Cachet With Rocket’s Success
